data.title: Wild Sage Salon
data.meta_description: Wild Sage Salon and Spa is located in beautiful downtown Waxahachie, Texas. Hair, Skin, Lashes, Massage Therapy, Brows, Waxing and more!
data.text: Sarah has been in the beauty industry since 2015 as a Makeup Artist and has been published in multiple magazines. In 2019 she became an esthetician, her passion is making sure her clients not only leave with healed skin, but also a healed mind. Her mission is to always create a safe space for others to feel safe and accepted when they visit her treatment room. Sarah was Awarded Ellis County Forty Under 40 in 2021 for her efforts and volunteer work she puts into the community. She has been recognized as "Waxahachie's Sweetheart" and once you meet her, you'll know why.
